trans-unit.source: Provides a phone call adapter class for the Wireless Markup Language (WML) device adapter set.
trans-unit.target: 提供的电话呼叫适配器类，用于无线标记语言 (WML) 设备适配器集。

trans-unit.source: For information about how to develop ASP.NET mobile applications, see the [www.asp.net/mobile](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=182900) Web site.

trans-unit.source: The WML call adapter renders the <xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.PhoneCall> by using a "tel:" URL on a phone with telephony capability.
trans-unit.target: WML 调用适配器呈现<xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.PhoneCall>通过使用"tel:"在电话服务功能手机上的 URL。</xref:System.Web.UI.MobileControls.PhoneCall>
